title: 149: Loaded draft positions,  Alabama vs. Clemson, talking QBs
itunes:title: 149: Loaded draft positions,  Alabama vs. Clemson, talking QBs
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the upcoming slate of Wild Card playoff games and re-draft the quarterbacks in the playoffs. DJ and Bucky also talk about which positions have the best crop for the 2017 NFL draft and make their picks for the Alabama vs. Clemson National Championship. Finally, there is a perfect landing spot for Colin Kapernick. The answer may surprise you.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
